{"tid":2172803,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"派路承諾視C.朗為核心 才能阻止他離隊","createTime":"2020-08-25T00:59:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T18:54:29.000Z","uid":173952,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"55a2fb9bc83c0188b4908d81925ca4912a78d81b","tid":2172803,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T00:59:46.000Z","msg":"意媒《拖連奴體育報》報導，在祖記新帥派路（Andrea Pirlo）與C.朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）會面，告知後者其是球隊未來核心計劃後，這有效地「阻止」了C.朗拿度的離開。<br />\n<br />\n  據此前報導，派路已與C.朗拿度及戴巴拿（Paulo Dybala）進行了會面，希望兩人都能成為球隊計劃的一部分，而C.朗拿度方面也向派路表達了留在球隊中的意願。<br />\n<br />\n  來自本月初記者Momblano的消息，C.朗拿度對於祖記在歐聯出局感到十分生氣，不滿現狀的他告知球會，若沙利（Maurizio Sarri）繼續執教，則他將考慮離開。而在沙利下台而派路出任新帥後，在雙方積極的會談之下，C.朗拿度被認為將會留下。"},{"pid":"38a03e4acbd5f20e8535f9ea4dd72eeea6372afd","tid":2172803,"uid":759,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:03:17.000Z","msg":"屍柒仲要踢多10年?"},{"pid":"12464b3316043c2225f372aecdc2c4f08bf323f9","tid":2172803,"uid":159818,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"38a03e4acbd5f20e8535f9ea4dd72eeea6372afd","tid":2172803,"uid":759,"like":6,"dislike":11,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:03:17.000Z","msg":"屍柒仲要踢多10年?"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:16:03.000Z","msg":"起碼五年啦，以後老d最多轉踢中場驚閪"},{"pid":"249c377c888354f120650cc01727901973da3077","tid":2172803,"uid":90521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:23:05.000Z","msg":"派路做左教練咩 之前有冇教過邊隊？"},{"pid":"f042feb61057b51d9c958833867397825eef6516","tid":2172803,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"249c377c888354f120650cc01727901973da3077","tid":2172803,"uid":90521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:23:05.000Z","msg":"派路做左教練咩 之前有冇教過邊隊？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T01:24:25.000Z","msg":"冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />